{"id":1528,"date":"2020-10-10T10:38:39","date_gmt":"2020-10-10T03:38:39","guid":{"rendered":"http:\/\/thocaca.com\/?p=1528"},"modified":"2021-08-22T08:15:29","modified_gmt":"2021-08-22T01:15:29","slug":"hoc-lich-su-theo-phuong-phap-moi-nho-lau-hon","status":"publish","type":"post","link":"https:\/\/thocaca.com\/blog\/2020\/10\/10\/hoc-lich-su-theo-phuong-phap-moi-nho-lau-hon\/","title":{"rendered":"H\u1ecdc l\u1ecbch s\u1eed theo ph\u01b0\u01a1ng ph\u00e1p m\u1edbi, nh\u1edb l\u00e2u h\u01a1n!~"},"content":{"rendered":"\n<p>Xin ch\u00e0o c\u00e1c b\u1ea1n, m\u00ecnh l\u1ea1i \u0111\u0103ng t\u00e0i li\u1ec7u cho m\u1ecdi ng\u01b0\u1eddi \u0111\u00e2y \u1ea1!<\/p>\n\n\n\n<p>M\u00ecnh m\u1edbi t\u00ecm \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c m\u1ed9t cu\u1ed1n s\u00e1ch h\u1ecdc l\u1ecbch s\u1eed v\u1edbi m\u1ed9t ph\u01b0\u01a1ng ph\u00e1p c\u1ef1c k\u00ec hay nh\u00e9. \u0110\u1ea3m b\u1ea3o c\u00e1c b\u1ea1n v\u00e0o h\u1ecdc th\u1eed l\u00e0 m\u00ea t\u00edt \u00e0. N\u00f3 d\u1ea1ng ch\u01a1i \u00f4 ch\u1eef gi\u1ed1ng nh\u01b0 V\u01b0\u1ee3t ch\u01b0\u1edbng ng\u1ea1i v\u1eadt c\u1ee7a \u0110\u01b0\u1eddng l\u00ean \u0111\u1ec9nh Olympia \u00e1.<\/p>\n\n\n\n<p>V\u00ed d\u1ee5 \u00f4n ph\u1ea7n n\u1ed9i dung Trung Qu\u1ed1c. N\u00f3 s\u1ebd cho c\u00e1c h\u00e0ng ngang, g\u1ee3i \u00fd c\u00e1c h\u00e0ng ngang \u0111\u00f3 s\u1ebd g\u1ed3m r\u1ea5t nhi\u1ec1u c\u00e2u h\u1ecfi li\u00ean quan \u0111\u1ebfn L\u1ecbch s\u1eed Trung Qu\u1ed1c. Sau khi c\u00e1c b\u1ea1n ho\u00e0n th\u00e0nh xong h\u00e0ng ngang s\u1ebd n\u00eau l\u00ean t\u1eeb kh\u00f3a. Gi\u1ea3i \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c t\u1eeb kh\u00f3a xem nh\u01b0 tr\u00f2 ch\u01a1i k\u1ebft th\u00fac. Ki\u1ec3u v\u1eeba h\u1ecdc v\u1eeba ch\u01a1i nh\u01b0 th\u1ebf n\u00e0y ch\u1eafc c\u00e1c b\u1ea1n m\u00ea t\u00edt nh\u1ec9?<\/p>\n\n\n\n<p>Hay l\u1eafm lu\u00f4n. Nhanh t\u1ea3i v\u1ec1 \u0111\u1ec3 h\u1ecdc v\u00e0 ch\u01a1i nh\u00e9&#8221;: <a href=\"https:\/\/drive.google.com\/file\/d\/0B3BjI_on1_SeTk15X3pTZGFpRXM\/view?usp=sharing\">T\u1ea0I \u0110\u00c2Y!<\/a><\/p>\n\n\n\n<p>Ch\u00fac c\u00e1c b\u1ea1n h\u1ecdc th\u1eadt t\u1ed1t hen!<\/p>\n<!-- AddThis Advanced Settings generic via filter on the_content --><!-- AddThis Share Buttons generic via filter on the_content -->","protected":false},"excerpt":{"rendered":"<div class=\"mh-excerpt\"><p>Xin ch\u00e0o c\u00e1c b\u1ea1n, m\u00ecnh l\u1ea1i \u0111\u0103ng t\u00e0i li\u1ec7u cho m\u1ecdi ng\u01b0\u1eddi \u0111\u00e2y \u1ea1! M\u00ecnh m\u1edbi t\u00ecm \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c m\u1ed9t cu\u1ed1n s\u00e1ch h\u1ecdc l\u1ecbch s\u1eed v\u1edbi <a class=\"mh-excerpt-more\" href=\"https:\/\/thocaca.com\/blog\/2020\/10\/10\/hoc-lich-su-theo-phuong-phap-moi-nho-lau-hon\/\" title=\"H\u1ecdc l\u1ecbch s\u1eed theo ph\u01b0\u01a1ng ph\u00e1p m\u1edbi, nh\u1edb l\u00e2u h\u01a1n!~\">[&#8230;]<\/a><!-- AddThis Advanced Settings generic via filter on get_the_excerpt --><!-- AddThis Share Buttons generic via filter on get_the_excerpt --><\/p>\n<\/div>","protected":false},"author":3,"featured_media":1529,"comment_status":"closed","ping_status":"open","sticky":false,"template":"","format":"standard","meta":[],"categories":[14,7,4],"tags":[51,83,102],"_links":{"self":[{"href":"https:\/\/thocaca.com\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/posts\/1528"}],"collection":[{"href":"https:\/\/thocaca.com\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/posts"}],"about":[{"href":"https:\/\/thocaca.com\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/types\/post"}],"author":[{"embeddable":true,"href":"https:\/\/thocaca.com\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/users\/3"}],"replies":[{"embeddable":true,"href":"https:\/\/thocaca.com\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/comments?post=1528"}],"version-history":[{"count":2,"href":"https:\/\/thocaca.com\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/posts\/1528\/revisions"}],"predecessor-version":[{"id":1531,"href":"https:\/\/thocaca.com\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/posts\/1528\/revisions\/1531"}],"wp:featuredmedia":[{"embeddable":true,"href":"https:\/\/thocaca.com\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/media\/1529"}],"wp:attachment":[{"href":"https:\/\/thocaca.com\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/media?parent=1528"}],"w